column7: I was happy with the service and tipped the packers for their work. But then I got to knowni have two big cartons (3.5x2 size self packed in advance) missing since the unloading time which I realised next day as it was very late by the time unloading and unpacking was completed. My calls next day were not returned by the packers and failed/unreplied emails to the lady who was otherwise available during shifting. It is very sad that post shifting, customer care is not available even after emails. This is not expected and it's cheating and thieving a customer who puts trust in Porter. Who's responsible for my loss here? No, I am not recommending Porter to anyone.

column7:
Shifting Experience. The professional Mr. Pandit who was assigned for moving some of my items from Vasant kunj (kishangarh) to Noida on 11/02/2023.

My experience with the Porter professional was not very unsatisfactory because of the following reasons:
1) the professional reported 1:30 hrs late
2) No packaging items were brought. 
3) His way of communication with customer wasn't polite AT ALL. 
4) He doesn't know how to Bubble wrap just a simple thing. 
My items includes 2 bags, inverter & with battery and window AC and bed side runner carpet. 
I booked for 5 cartoon box. He didn't bring any. 
So the other items were taken in loose not packed inside the box. 
He refuse to packed the items in my room stating that the items will be difficult to carry it downstairs. Whereas I strongly mentioned to him that - I DO NOT WANT MY ITEMS TO GO OUT OF THE ROOM UNPACKED. He denied. 
So I let him go with his wishes. 

Despite of my request to call and notify me once the loading is completed.  He didn't care to update me. He reaches the destination very late.

I tried calling him continuously  to asked if he has loaded all the items carefully. He didn't attend to my calls. 
So I had to chanel my calls toward the Porter customer care just to speak with him. 

Overall experience with the professional Pandit, I would not recommend anyone now I am not sure if I should use the service again for my house shifting or should go for other company. 

Thanking you for providing this platform to share the our issues. 
Best regards 
Phyaziine Ranjeeta
